of the Licenses page when logged in to wordfence.com if you need more than one.','This key may already be used on several sites. To avoid scan scheduling issues and other problems, you should get a new key or remove it from the other sites.'=>'This key may already be used on several sites. To avoid scan scheduling issues and other problems, you should get a new key or remove it from the other sites.','each Wordfence installation should have a unique key'=>'each Wordfence installation should have a unique key','You may close this alert and try again later, or click the button below to register for a new free Wordfence license.'=>'You may close this alert and try again later, or click the button below to register for a new free Wordfence license.','There was an error while downgrading to a free license.'=>'There was an error while downgrading to a free license.','A free license key could not be fetched from Wordfence: %s'=>'A free license key could not be fetched from Wordfence: %s','WORDFENCE_WAF_PREPEND_DIRECTORY path constant'=>'WORDFENCE_WAF_PREPEND_DIRECTORY path constant','a Wordfence Central user'=>'a Wordfence Central user','Disconnected on %1$s'=>'Disconnected on %1$s','Check for a server outage.'=>'Check for a server outage.','Manage'=>'Manage','Recording (all events)'=>'Recording (all events)','Recording (significant events only)'=>'Recording (significant events only)','Not recording'=>'Not recording','Not recording (Central disconnected)'=>'Not recording (Central disconnected)','Disabled (premium feature)'=>'Disabled (premium feature)','Not connected'=>'Not connected','Connection not finished'=>'Connection not finished','Connection'=>'Connection','These options let you choose which site events to record in the audit log. When enabled and your site is connected to Wordfence Central, these events are automatically sent to Central to prevent any tampering by an attacker. When <strong>Audit Log logging mode</strong> is set to "Significant Events", all events except content changes will be recorded. "All Events" will include content-related events and may be used to monitor for unauthorized post or page changes. "Preview" and "Disabled" modes do not send any events to Central.'=>'These options let you choose which site events to record in the audit log. When enabled and your site is connected to Wordfence Central, these events are automatically sent to Central to prevent any tampering by an attacker. When <strong>Audit Log logging mode</strong> is set to "Significant Events", all events except content changes will be recorded. "All Events" will include content-related events and may be used to monitor for unauthorised post or page changes. "Preview" and "Disabled" modes do not send any events to Central.','The most recently-detected events on this site are listed below. When the audit log is enabled and your site is connected to Wordfence Central, full details of each event can be found on Central. This includes information such as record IDs, version numbers, and which modifications were made. Log entries in preview mode are only stored locally.'=>'The most recently-detected events on this site are listed below. When the audit log is enabled and your site is connected to Wordfence Central, full details of each event can be found on Central. This includes information such as record IDs, version numbers, and which modifications were made. Log entries in preview mode are only stored locally.','You are running WordPress version %1$s that is not supported by Wordfence %2$s. Wordfence features will not be available until WordPress has been upgraded. We recommend using the current version of WordPress, but Wordfence will run on WordPress version %3$s at a minimum.'=>'You are running WordPress version %1$s that is not supported by Wordfence %2$s. Wordfence features will not be available until WordPress has been upgraded. We recommend using the current version of WordPress, but Wordfence will run on WordPress version %3$s at a minimum.','The Wordfence Audit Log is a premium feature that records a history of events on your site to assist in monitoring for unauthorized actions or signs of compromise. Events can include everything from user creation and editing to plugin/theme installation and updates. All data captured for relevant events is saved remotely to Wordfence Central to prevent any tampering that may interfere with post-incident analysis and response.'=>'The Wordfence Audit Log is a premium feature that records a history of events on your site to assist in monitoring for unauthorised actions or signs of compromise. Events can include everything from user creation and editing to plugin/theme installation and updates. All data captured for relevant events is saved remotely to Wordfence Central to prevent any tampering that may interfere with post-incident analysis and response.','Display Audit Log menu option'=>'Display Audit Log menu option','Preview'=>'Preview','Are you sure you want to restore the default settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page.'=>'Are you sure you want to restore the default settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page.','Audit Log Options'=>'Audit Log Options','Display "Audit Log" menu item'=>'Display "Audit Log" menu item','Unknown Events'=>'Unknown Events','Plugin/Themes/Updates'=>'Plugin/Themes/Updates','User/Permissions'=>'User/Permissions','Authentication'=>'Authentication','No Events Detected'=>'No Events Detected','Events'=>'Events','Recent Event Summary'=>'Recent Event Summary','The Wordfence Audit Log is designed to monitor all changes and actions in security-sensitive areas of the site. Actions such as user creation, plugin installation and activation, changes to settings, and similar are all logged with relevant contextual information for later review or forensic analysis. Additionally, the log is securely saved outside of the site on Wordfence Central (sample below) to avoid tampering or deletion by malicious actors.'=>'The Wordfence Audit Log is designed to monitor all changes and actions in security-sensitive areas of the site. Actions such as user creation, plugin installation and activation, changes to settings, and similar are all logged with relevant contextual information for later review or forensic analysis. Additionally, the log is securely saved outside of the site on Wordfence Central (sample below) to avoid tampering or deletion by malicious actors.','Log Security Events to an Off-Site Audit Log on Wordfence Central'=>'Log Security Events to an Off-Site Audit Log on Wordfence Central','The audit log is currently recording all monitored events to Wordfence Central, including content changes, user actions and changes, site modifications, and Wordfence configuration updates.'=>'The audit log is currently recording all monitored events to Wordfence Central, including content changes, user actions and changes, site modifications, and Wordfence configuration updates.','Audit log mode: All events'=>'Audit log mode: All events','The audit log is currently recording all significant events to Wordfence Central, which includes user actions and updates, site modifications, and Wordfence configuration changes.'=>'The audit log is currently recording all significant events to Wordfence Central, which includes user actions and updates, site modifications, and Wordfence configuration changes.','Audit log mode: Significant events only'=>'Audit log mode: Significant events only','The Audit Log has failed to successfully send events for two days. Please verify the connection with Wordfence Central, connectivity to the Wordfence servers, and that the database has no damaged tables.'=>'The Audit Log has failed to successfully send events for two days. Please verify the connection with Wordfence Central, connectivity to the Wordfence servers, and that the database has no damaged tables.','Audit log mode: Malfunctioning'=>'Audit log mod