taging). We recommend disconnecting this site only, which will leave the matching site still connected.','Your site is currently linked to Wordfence Central under a different site URL.'=>'Your site is currently linked to Wordfence Central under a different site URL.','All associated Wordfence Central connection data has been removed from the local database.'=>'All associated Wordfence Central connection data has been removed from the local database.','If you use external services that may send POST requests without these headers, do not use this option, as they will be blocked.'=>'If you use external services that may send POST requests without these headers, do not use this option, as they will be blocked.','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.','Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'Login failed with status code 503. Please contact the site administrator.','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>ERROR</strong>: Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.','Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'Login failed with status code 403. Please contact the site administrator.','Thank you for providing your feedback on Wordfence Security'=>'Thank you for providing your feedback on Wordfence Security','Submit Feedback'=>'Submit Feedback','What can we do to improve Wordfence Security?'=>'What can we do to improve Wordfence Security?','Leave Review'=>'Leave Review','Please consider leaving us a 5-star review on wordpress.org. Your review helps other members of the WordPress community find plugins that fit their needs.'=>'Please consider leaving us a 5-star review on wordpress.org. Your review helps other members of the WordPress community find 