ror'=>'Update Check Error','Acknowledge User'=>'Acknowledge User','We could not find that issue in the database.'=>'We could not find that issue in the database.','Update Check Encountered Error on \'%s\''=>'Update Check Encountered Error on \'%s\'','Update Check Encountered Error'=>'Update Check Encountered Error','Wordfence cannot detect if this plugin/theme is up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in the plugin.'=>'Wordfence cannot detect if this plugin/theme is up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in the plugin.','Wordfence cannot detect if the installed plugins and themes are up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in one or more plugins/themes.'=>'Wordfence cannot detect if the installed plugins and themes are up to date. This might be caused by a PHP compatibility issue in one or more plugins/themes.','The update check performed during the scan encountered an error: %s'=>'The update check performed during the scan encountered an error: %s','You must select either "Yes" or "No"'=>'You must select either "Yes" or "No"','Would you like WordPress security and vulnerability alerts sent to you via email?'=>'Would you like WordPress security and vulnerability alerts sent to you via email?','The Wordfence 2FA Code can be found within the authenticator app you used when first activating two-factor authentication. You may also use one of your recovery codes.'=>'The Wordfence 2FA Code can be found within the authenticator app you used when first activating two-factor authentication. You may also use one of your recovery codes.','If you cannot complete the setup process, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'If you cannot complete the setup process, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>','The Plugin "%s" has been removed from wordpress.org but is still installed on your site.'=>'The Plugin "%s" has been removed from WordPress.org but is still installed on your site.','Search All Options'=>'Search All Options','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to authenticate. Please try again.'=>'<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to authenticate. Please try again.','Log In'=>'Log In','Remember for 30 days'=>'Remember for 30 days','Wordfence 2FA Code'=>'Wordfence 2FA Code','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.'=>'<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.','An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.'=>'An error was encountered while trying to send the message. Please try again.','Message to Support'=>'Message to Support','Skipping inaccessible directory: %s'=>'Skipping inaccessible directory: %s','Below is a sample of these recent attacks:'=>'Below is a sample of these recent attacks:','Wordfence is blocking these attacks, and we\'re sending this notice to make you aware that there is a higher volume of the attacks than usual. Additionally, the Wordfence Real-Time IP Blocklist can block known attackers\' IP addresses automatically for Premium users, including any probing requests that may not be malicious on their own. All Wordfence users can also opt to block the attacking IPs manually if desired. As always, be sure to watch your scan results and keep your plugins, themes and WordPress core version updated.'=>'Wordfence is blocking these attacks, and we\'re sending this notice to make you aware that there is a higher volume of the attacks than usual. Additionally, the Wordfence Real-Time IP Blocklist can block known attackers\' IP addresses automatically for Premium users, including any probing requests that may not be malicious on their own. All Wordfence users can also opt to block the attacking IPs manually if desired. As always, be sure to watch your scan results and keep your plugins, themes and WordPress core version updated.','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall has blocked %1$d attacks over the last %2$s.'=>'The Wordfence Web Application Firewall has blocked %1$d attacks over the last %2$s.','North Macedonia, Republic of'=>'North Macedonia, Republic of','WAF Loaded Successfully'=>'WAF Loaded Successfully','Outdated plugin scan adjusted invalid return value in plugins_api filter for %s'=>'Outdated plugin scan adjusted invalid return value in plugins_api filter for %s','Unable to output phpinfo content because it is disabled'=>'Unable to output phpinfo content because it is disabled','Vulnerability Severity'=>'Vulnerability Severity','Show User Counts'=>'Show User Counts','User counts are currently disabled as the most recent attempt to count users failed to complete successfully.'=>'User counts are currently disabled as the most recent attempt to count users failed to complete successfully.','User counts are hidden by default on sites with large numbers of users in order to improve performance.'=>'User counts are hidden by default on sites with large numbers of users in order to improve performance.','Custom Capabilities / Multiple Roles'=>'Custom Capabilities / Multiple Roles','An error was detected with this site\'s configuration that is preventing a successful connection to Wordfence Central. Disconnecting from Central <a href="%s">on the Wordfence Dashboard</a> and reconnecting may resolve it. If the issue persists, please contact Wordfence support.'=>'An error was detected with this site\'s configuration that is preventing a successful connection to Wordfence Central. Disconnecting from Central <a href="%s">on the Wordfence Dashboard</a> and reconnecting may resolve it. If the issue persists, please contact Wordfence support.','Fetching token for Wordfence Central authentication due to configuration issue.'=>'Fetching token for Wordfence Central authentication due to configuration issue.','reCAPTCHA'=>'reCAPTCHA','When enabled, the 2FA management interface embedded through the WooCommerce integration or via a shortcode will use a vertical stacked layout as opposed to horizontal columns. Adjust this setting as appropriate to match your theme. This may be overridden using the "stacked" attribute for individual shortcodes.'=>'When enabled, the 2FA management interface embedded through the WooCommerce integration or via a shortcode will use a vertical stacked layout as opposed to horizontal columns. Adjust this setting as appropriate to match your theme. This may be overridden using the "stacked" attribute for individual shortcodes.','Use single-column layout for WooCommerce/shortcode 2FA management interface'=>'Use single-column layout for WooCommerce/shortcode 2FA management interface','When enabled, the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode may be used to provide access for users to manage 2FA settings on custom pages.'=>'When enabled, the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode may be used to provide access for users to manage 2FA settings on custom pages.','2FA management shortcode'=>'2FA management shortcode','When enabled, a Wordfence 2FA tab will be added to the WooCommerce account menu which will provide access for users to manage 2FA settings outside of the WordPress admin area. Testing the WooCommerce account interface after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure theme compatibility.'=>'When enabled, a Wordfence 2FA tab will be added to the WooCommerce account menu which will provide access for users to manage 2FA settings outside of the WordPress admin area. Testing the WooCommerce account interface after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure theme compatibility.','2FA Notifications'=>'2FA Notifications','Requiring 2FA for customers is not recommended as some customers may experience difficulties setting up or using two-factor authentication. Instead, using the "Optional" mode for users with the customer role is recommended which will allow customers to enable 2FA, but will not require them to do so.'=>'Requiring 2FA for customers is not recommended as some customers may experience difficulties setting up or using two-factor authentication. Instead, using the "Optional" mode for users with the customer role is recommended which will allow customers to enable 2FA, but will not require them to do so.','In order to use 2FA with the WooCommerce customer role, you must either enable the "WooCommerce integration" option or use the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode to provide customers with access to the 2FA management interface. The default interface is only available through WordPress admin pages which are not accessible to users in the customer role.'=>'In order to use 2FA with the WooCommerce customer role, you must either enable the "WooCommerce integration" option or use the "wordfence_2fa_management" shortcode to provide customers with access to the 2FA management interface. The default interface is only available through WordPress admin pages which are not accessible to users in the customer role.','Wordfence 2FA'=>'Wordfence 2FA','<html><body><p>You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %1$s.</p><p><a href="%2$s">Configure 2FA</a></p></body></html>'=>'<html><body><p>You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %1$s.</p><p><a href="%2$s">Configure 2FA</a></p></body></html>','Send an email to users with the selected role to notify them of the grace period for enabling 2FA. Select the desired role and optionally specify the URL to be sent in the email to setup 2FA. If left blank, the URL defaults to the standard wordpress login and Wordfence’s Two-Factor Authentication plugin page. For example, if using WooCommerce, input the relative URL of the account page.'=>'Send an email to users with the selected role to notify them of the grace period for enabling 2FA. Select the desired role and optionally specify the URL to be sent in the email to setup 2FA. If left blank, the URL defaults to the standard WordPress login and Wordfence’s Two-Factor Authentication plugin page. For example, if using WooCommerce, input the relative URL of the account page.','Show Wordfence 2FA menu on WooCommerce Account page'=>'Show Wordfence 2FA menu on WooCommerce Account page','WooCommerce integration'=>'WooCommerce integration','WooCommerce & Custom Integrations'=>'WooCommerce & Custom Integrations','You do not have permission to manage 2FA settings for your account.'=>'You do not have permission to manage 2FA settings for your account.','Permission Denied'=>'Permission Denied','Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your account. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.'=>'Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your account. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.','2FA Relative URL (optional)'=>'2FA Relative URL (optional)','2FA Role'=>'2FA Role','The specified URL is invalid.'=>'The specified URL is invalid.','Are you sure you want to delete the selected Wordfence data? If you reactivate Wordfence later, deleted settings and history cannot be recovered.'=>'Are you sure you want to delete the selected Wordfence data? If you reactivate Wordfence later, deleted settings and history cannot be recovered.','Delete Wordfence Data?'=>'Delete Wordfence Data?','Extended Protection Still Enabled'=>'Extended Protection Still Enabled','Deactivate and Delete Data'=>'Deactivate and Delete Data','Deactivate Wordfence'=>'Deactivate Wordfence','Invalid option specified'=>'Invalid option specified','Delete Login Security tables and 2FA codes, but keep Wordfence tables and data'=>'Delete Login Security tables and 2FA codes, but keep Wordfence tables and data','Delete Wordfence tables and data, but keep Login Security tables and 2FA codes'=>'Delete Wordfence tables and data, but keep Login Security tables and 2FA codes','The Wordfence firewall is still optimized. You should remove the firewall\'s extended protection before deleting to avoid PHP errors if some firewall files cannot be removed, or if PHP\'s "auto_prepend_file" setting is cached.'=>'The Wordfence firewall is still optimised. You should remove the firewall\'s extended protection before deleting to avoid PHP errors if some firewall files cannot be removed, or if PHP\'s "auto_prepend_file" setting is cached.','Keep all Wordfence tables and data'=>'Keep all Wordfence tables and data','Install your license to finish activating Wordfence.'=>'Install your license to finish activating Wordfence.','You must install a license to continue using Wordfence.'=>'You must install a license to continue using Wordfence.','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to dismiss the notice. Please try again.'=>'An unexpected error occurred while attempting to dismiss the notice. Please try again.','You will be reminded again in 12 hours.'=>'You will be reminded again in 12 hours.','Notice Dismissed'=>'Notice Dismissed','Remind Me Later'=>'Remind Me Later','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to configure Wordfence to delete its data on deactivation.'=>'An unexpected error occurred while attempting to configure Wordfence to delete its data on deactivation.','You are about to deactivate Wordfence. Would you like to delete its data or keep it in place?'=>'You are about to deactivate Wordfence. Would you like to delete its data or keep it in place?','Delete all Wordfence tables and data'=>'Delete all Wordfence tables and data','This could be caused by a database problem. You may need to repair your "wfconfig" database table or fix your database user\'s privileges if they have changed recently, or you may need to reinstall Wordfence. Please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence support<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> if you need help.'=>'This could be caused by a database problem. You may need to repair your "wfconfig" database table or fix your database user\'s privileges if they have changed recently, or you may need to reinstall Wordfence. Please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence support<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> if you need help.','Please try again. If the problem persists, please <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence Support<span class="screen-reader-text">(opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'Please try again. If the problem persists, please <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence Support<span class="screen-reader-text">(opens in new tab)</span></a>','An error occurred while installing your license key.'=>'An error occurred while installing your license key.','Congratulations! Wordfence Free is now active on your website.'=>'Congratulations! Wordfence Free is now active on your website.','Congratulations! Wordfence Care is now active on your website. Please note that some Care features are not enabled by default.'=>'Congratulations! Wordfence Care is now active on your website. Please note that some Care features are not enabled by default.','Care License Installed'=>'Care License Installed','Congratulations! Wordfence Response is now active on your website. Please note that some Response features are not enabled by default.'=>'Congratulations! Wordfence Response is now active on your website. Please note that some Response features are not enabled by default.','Response License Installed'=>'Response License Installed','Get a new license'=>'Get a new license','This is where future security alerts for your website will be sent. This can also be changed in Global Options.'=>'This is where future security alerts for your website will be sent. This can also be changed in Global Options.','Please enter a valid email address'=>'Please enter a valid email address','Email'=>'Email','Install an existing license'=>'Install an existing license','Get Your Wordfence License'=>'Get Your Wordfence License','Register with Wordfence to secure your site with the latest threat intelligence.'=>'Register with Wordfence to secure your site with the latest threat intelligence.','Wordfence\'s license key is missing.'=>'Wordfence\'s license key is missing.','An unknown error occurred.'=>'An unknown error occurred.','Install Wordfence'=>'Install Wordfence','An error occurred while retrieving your license information from the Wordfence servers. Please ensure that your server can reach www.wordfence.com on port 443.'=>'An error occurred while retrieving your license information from the Wordfence servers. Please ensure that your server can reach www.wordfence.com on port 443.','The link you used to access this page has expired, has already been used, or is otherwise invalid.'=>'The link you used to access this page has expired, has already been used, or is otherwise invalid.','Too many installation requests have been made from your IP address. Please try again later.'=>'Too many installation requests have been made from your IP address. Please try again later.','Wordfence is already installed on this site. If you need to replace the current license, you may do so by visiting the "All Options" page of the Wordfence menu.'=>'Wordfence is already installed on this site. If you need to replace the current license, you may do so by visiting the "All Options" page of the Wordfence menu.','If this option is disabled, Wordfence can look up countries for visitor IP addresses using a local database, but cannot look up regions or cities'=>'If this option is disabled, Wordfence can look up countries for visitor IP addresses using a local database, but cannot look up regions or cities','Scan Stage Failed'=>'Scan Stage Failed','Wordfence will make up to %d attempts to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if one of these attempts is successful.'=>'Wordfence will make up to %d attempts to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if one of these attempts is successful.','Wordfence will make one attempt to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if this attempt is successful.'=>'Wordfence will make one attempt to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if this attempt is successful.','Attempting to resume scan stage (%d attempt(s) remaining)...'=>'Attempting to resume scan stage (%d attempt(s) remaining)...','Cached result for scan start test: %s'=>'Cached result for scan start test: %s','To protect your site from this vulnerability, the safest option is to deactivate and completely remove "%1$s" until a patched version is available. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'To protect your site from this vulnerability, the safest option is to deactivate and completely remove "%1$s" until a patched version is available. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>','The Plugin "%s" has a security vulnerability.'=>'The Plugin "%s" has a security vulnerability.','Invalid number of scan resume attempts specified: %d'=>'Invalid number of scan resume attempts specified: %d','Maximum number of attempts to resume each scan stage'=>'Maximum number of attempts to resume each scan stage','Look up visitor IP locations via Wordfence servers'=>'Look up visitor IP locations via Wordfence servers','This option requires cURL. (This may have no effect on some old PHP or cURL versions.)'=>'This option requires cURL. (This may have no effect on some old PHP or cURL versions.)','Use only IPv4 to start scans'=>'Use only IPv4 to start scans','UA/Hostname/Referrer/IP Range not allowed'=>'UA/Hostname/Referrer/IP Range not allowed','Automatic updates enabled'=>'Automatic updates enabled','Automatic updates disabled'=>'Automatic updates disabled','Disables automatic updates'=>'Disables automatic updates','Cron is enabled'=>'Cron is enabled','Cron is disabled'=>'Cron is disabled','This diagnostic requires cURL'=>'This diagnostic requires cURL','This diagnostic is unavailable as cURL appears to be supported, but was not used by WordPress for this request'=>'This diagnostic is unavailable as cURL appears to be supported, but was not used by WordPress for this request','This likely indicates that the server either does not support IPv6 or does not have an IPv6 address assigned or associated with the domain. Original error message: %s'=>'This likely indicates that the server either does not support IPv6 or does not have an IPv6 address assigned or associated with the domain. Original error message: %s','IPv6 DNS resolution failed'=>'IPv6 DNS resolution failed','When enabled, the last login timestamp will be displayed for each user on the WP Users page. When used in conjunction with reCAPTCHA, the most recent score will also be displayed for each user.'=>'When enabled, the last login timestamp will be displayed for each user on the WP Users page. When used in conjunction with reCAPTCHA, the most recent score will also be displayed for each user.','Show last login column on WP Users page'=>'Show last login column on WP Users page','Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA','Login Security: Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'Login Security: Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA','Ignoring invalid scan file child: %s'=>'Ignoring invalid scan file child: %s','Ignoring invalid base scan file: %s'=>'Ignoring invalid base scan file: %s','Ignoring invalid expected scan file: %s'=>'Ignoring invalid expected scan file: %s','Ignoring invalid scan path: %s'=>'Ignoring invalid scan path: %s','This was a premium license key, but it is no longer valid, so premium features are disabled. You can either remove the invalid key and continue using Wordfence\'s free features, or enter a new premium key to upgrade. If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>.'=>'This was a premium license key, but it is no longer valid, so premium features are disabled. You can either remove the invalid key and continue using Wordfence\'s free features, or enter a new premium key to upgrade. If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>.','Remove Invalid License'=>'Remove Invalid License','Premium License Deactivated'=>'Premium License Deactivated','Unable to read file contents'=>'Unable to read file contents','Empty file path provided'=>'Empty file path provided','This link has expired. Refresh the scan results page and try again.'=>'This link has expired. Refresh the scan results page and try again.','Edit Wordfence Options'=>'Edit Wordfence Options','The site admin can change this option.'=>'The site admin can change this option.','Application Passwords'=>'Application Passwords','Sign up for Wordfence Care and we\'ll take care of it. Our security experts will clean your site, resolve the infection, and perform a security audit. Get hands-on support with any security issue including help installing, configuring and optimizing Wordfence.'=>'Sign up for Wordfence Care and we\'ll take care of it. Our security experts will clean your site, resolve the infection, and perform a security audit. Get hands-on support with any security issue including help installing, configuring and optimising Wordfence.','Wordfence Firewall & Response License Enabled'=>'Wordfence Firewall & Response License Enabled','Wordfence Firewall & Care License Enabled'=>'Wordfence Firewall & Care License Enabled','Need help with a security issue?'=>'Need help with a security issue?','Learn More About Wordfence Response'=>'Learn More About Wordfence Response','Learn More About Wordfence Care'=>'Learn More About Wordfence Care','Sign up for Wordfence Care today and get expert help with any security issue. Wordfence Care is for business owners who put a premium on their time. With Wordfence Care, we take care of it, so that you can focus on your customers. Check out Wordfence Response for mission-critical WordPress websites.'=>'Sign up for Wordfence Care today and get expert help with any security issue. Wordfence Care is for business owners who put a premium on their time. With Wordfence Care, we take care of it, so that you can focus on your customers. Check out Wordfence Response for mission-critical WordPress websites.','Wordfence Scan & Response License Enabled'=>'Wordfence Scan & Response License Enabled','Wordfence Scan & Care License Enabled'=>'Wordfence Scan & Care License Enabled','We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the Wordfence License Terms and Conditions, the Services Subscription Agreement, and Terms of Service, and read and acknowledge the Wordfence Privacy Policy by clicking Review.'=>'We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the Wordfence License Terms and Conditions, the Services Subscription Agreement, and Terms of Service, and read and acknowledge the Wordfence Privacy Policy by clicking Review.','Confirm Reset'=>'Confirm Reset','Click here to manage your Wordfence licenses'=>'Click here to manage your Wordfence licenses','Reset site to a free license'=>'Reset site to a free license','%s License Active'=>'%s License Active','%s License Expired'=>'%s License Expired','Upgrade to Response'=>'Upgrade to Response','Upgrade to Care'=>'Upgrade to Care','Free'=>'Free','Wordfence Free'=>'Wordfence Free','Wordfence Premium'=>'Wordfence Premium','Wordfence Response'=>'Wordfence Response','Care'=>'Care','Wordfence Care'=>'Wordfence Care','Upgrade to a 24/7 1-hour response time with Wordfence Response'=>'Upgrade to a 24/7 1-hour response time with Wordfence Response','Upgrade to hands-on support with Wordfence Care'=>'Upgrade to hands-on support with Wordfence Care','As a Wordfence Premium customer you\'re entitled to paid support via our ticketing system. Our senior support engineers respond to Premium tickets during regular business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.'=>'As a Wordfence Premium customer you\'re entitled to paid support via our ticketing system. Our senior support engineers respond to Premium tickets during regular business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.','As a Wordfence Care customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support and have access to our incident response team. Our senior support engineers and incident response team respond to requests quickly within business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and can sign-in to your site on request to assist with complex issues.'=>'As a Wordfence Care customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support and have access to our incident response team. Our senior support engineers and incident response team respond to requests quickly within business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and can sign-in to your site on request to assist with complex issues.','As a Wordfence Response customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support 24 hours a day 365 days a year. Our incident response team is available out of hours to handle urgent issues and security incidents. Our customer support team is available during business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) for product assistance. Both teams can sign-in to your site to assist, on request.'=>'As a Wordfence Response customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support 24 hours a day 365 days a year. Our incident response team is available out of hours to handle urgent issues and security incidents. Our customer support team is available during business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) for product assistance. Both teams can sign-in to your site to assist, on request.','Learn about Wordfence Care and Wordfence Response'=>'Learn about Wordfence Care and Wordfence Response','%s Enabled'=>'%s Enabled','Learn about Wordfence Response'=>'Learn about Wordfence Response','Automatic uninstallation cannot be completed, but you may still be able to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">manually uninstall extended protection<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'Automatic uninstallation cannot be completed, but you may still be able to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">manually uninstall extended protection<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.','If you cannot complete the uninstall process, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'If you cannot complete the uninstall process, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>','If you don\'t recognize this file, please <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact us on the WordPress support forums<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> before proceeding.'=>'If you don\'t recognise this file, please <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact us on the WordPress support forums<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> before proceeding.','You can find more details on alternative setup steps, including installation on SiteGround or for multiple sites sharing a single php.ini, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">in our documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'You can find more details on alternative setup steps, including installation on SiteGround or for multiple sites sharing a single php.ini, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">in our documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.','You can log in to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> to accept the updated terms and privacy policy for all of your license keys at once.'=>'You can log in to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> to accept the updated terms and Privacy Policy for all of your license keys at once.','For most sites, we recommend allowing access from the United States, where Google and other benign crawlers are generally located. Many well-known crawlers also have locations in Europe, so be careful when blocking other countries, especially if you have not seen significant attacks from them.'=>'For most sites, we recommend allowing access from the United States, where Google and other benign crawlers are generally located. Many well-known crawlers also have locations in Europe, so be careful when blocking other countries, especially if you have not seen significant attacks from them.','U.S. Blocked'=>'U.S. Blocked','Error Saving Block'=>'Error Saving Block','Allow a grace period for this user prior to requiring Wordfence 2FA'=>'Allow a grace period for this user prior to requiring Wordfence 2FA','2FA Grace Period'=>'2FA Grace Period','View users'=>'View users','When enabled, reCAPTCHA and 2FA prompt support will be added to WooCommerce login and registration forms in addition to the default WordPress forms. Testing WooCommerce forms after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure plugin compatibility.'=>'When enabled, reCAPTCHA and 2FA prompt support will be added to WooCommerce login and registration forms in addition to the default WordPress forms. Testing WooCommerce forms after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure plugin compatibility.','Page '=>'Page ','N/A'=>'N/A','Page %d is out of range'=>'Page %d is out of range','No users found in the %1$s state for the %2$s role'=>'No users found in the %1$s state for the %2$s role','2FA is not required for the %s role'=>'2FA is not required for the %s role','This page only shows users and roles on the main site of this network'=>'This page only shows users and roles on the main site of this network','Send Anyway'=>'Send Anyway','Notify'=>'Notify','For roles that require 2FA, users will have this many days to set up 2FA. Failure to set up 2FA during this period will result in the user losing account access. This grace period will apply to new users from the time of account creation. For existing users, this grace period will apply relative to the time at which the requirement is implemented. This grace period will not automatically apply to admins and must be manually enabled for each admin user.'=>'For roles that require 2FA, users will have this many days to set up 2FA. Failure to set up 2FA during this period will result in the user losing account access. This grace period will apply to new users from the time of account creation. For existing users, this grace period will apply relative to the time at which the requirement is implemented. This grace period will not automatically apply to admins and must be manually enabled for each admin user.','Setting the grace period to 0 will prevent users in roles where 2FA is required, including newly created users, from logging in if they have not already enabled two-factor authentication.'=>'Setting the grace period to 0 will prevent users in roles where 2FA is required, including newly created users, from logging in if they have not already enabled two-factor authentication.','Error Resetting NTP'=>'Error Resetting NTP','NTP will be automatically disabled after 1 more attempt.'=>'NTP will be automatically disabled after 1 more attempt.','NTP will be automatically disabled after %d more attempts.'=>'NTP will be automatically disabled after %d more attempts.','NTP updates are currently failing.'=>'NTP updates are currently failing.','NTP is currently <strong>enabled</strong>.'=>'NTP is currently <strong>enabled</strong>.','Reset'=>'Reset','NTP was manually disabled.'=>'NTP was manually disabled.','NTP is currently disabled as %d subsequent attempts have failed.'=>'NTP is currently disabled as %d subsequent attempts have failed.','The constant WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP is defined which disables NTP entirely. Remove this constant or set it to a falsy value to enable NTP.'=>'The constant WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP is defined which disables NTP entirely. Remove this constant or set it to a falsy value to enable NTP.','Note: This feature requires a free site key and secret for the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 Service</a>. To set up new reCAPTCHA keys, log into your Google account and go to the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA admin page</a>.'=>'Note: This feature requires a free site key and secret for the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 Service</a>. To set up new reCAPTCHA keys, log into your Google account and go to the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA admin page</a>.','NTP is a protocol that allows for remote time synchronization. Wordfence Login Security uses this protocol to ensure that it has the most accurate time which is necessary for TOTP-based two-factor authentication.'=>'NTP is a protocol that allows for remote time synchronisation. Wordfence Login Security uses this protocol to ensure that it has the most accurate time which is necessary for TOTP-based two-factor authentication.','2FA Roles'=>'2FA Roles','An error was encountered while trying to disable NTP. Please try again.'=>'An error was encountered while trying to disable NTP. Please try again.','Error Disabling NTP'=>'Error Disabling NTP','An error was encountered while trying to reset the NTP state. Please try again.'=>'An error was encountered while trying to reset the NTP state. Please try again.','Two-factor authentication will be required for your account beginning <strong>%s</strong>'=>'Two-factor authentication will be required for your account beginning <strong>%s</strong>','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to revoke the grace period.'=>'An unexpected error occurred while attempting to revoke the grace period.','Revoke Grace Period'=>'Revoke Grace Period','Two-factor authentication is required for your account, but has not been configured.'=>'Two-factor authentication is required for your account, but has not been configured.','Manage Settings'=>'Manage Settings','WooCommerce appears to be installed, but the Wordfence Login Security WooCommerce integration is not currently enabled. Without this feature, WooCommerce forms will not support all functionality provided by Wordfence Login Security, including CAPTCHA for the login page and user registration.